|22|format=dmy}}}}\n|Ruslan Chagaev vs. [[Kali Meehan]]\n|{{center|3,100,000}}\n|ZDF\n|<ref name=\"meehan-chagaev\">[https://www.abendblatt.de/sport/article106514340/Mit-Chagaev-und-Tajbert-in-der-Erfolgsspur.html Der eine bleibt Champion, der andere kann es werden - die Zukunft des Hamburger Profiboxstalls Universum bleibt dennoch ungekl\u00e4rt] (ger.)</ref>\n|-\n|{{center|{{dts|2015|July|11|format=dmy}}}}\n|Ruslan Chagaev vs. [[Francesco Pianeta]]\n|{{center|2,060,000}}\n|[[Sat.1]]\n|<ref name=\"pianeta-chagaev\">[https://www.eurosport.de/boxen/rusland-chagaev-gewinnt-den-wba-kampf-gegen-francesco-pianeta-in-der-ersten-runde_sto4818027/story.shtml Rusland Chagaev gewinnt den WBA-Kampf gegen Francesco Pianeta in der ersten Runde] (ger.)</ref>\n|-\n!\n! Total viewership\n! 30,680,000\n!\n!\n|}\n\n==See also==\n*[[List of world heavyweight boxing champions]]\n*[[List of left-handed boxers]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Boxrec|id=024358}}\n\n{{s-start-collapsible|header={{s-sports}} }}\n{{s-text|style=background:#C1D8FF; font-weight: bold;|text=Regional boxing titles}}\n{{s-bef|rows=2|before=[[Volodymyr Virchis]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[World Boxing Association|WBA]] Inter-Continental<br>[[heavyweight]] champion\n|years=11 March 2006 \u2013 15 July 2006<br>Vacated}}\n{{s-vac|next=[[Taras Bidenko]]}}\n{{s-break}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[World Boxing Organization|WBO]] Inter-Continental<br>heavyweight champion\n|years=11 March 2006 \u2013 April 2006<br>Vacated}}\n{{s-vac|next=[[Alexander Dimitrenko]]}}\n{{s-break}}\n{{s-vac|last=[[Sultan Ibragimov]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=WBO Asia Pacific<br>heavyweight champion\n|years=15 July 2006 \u2013 March 2007<br>Vacated}}\n{{s-vac|next=[[Denis Bakhtov]]}}\n{{s-new}}\n{{s-ttl|title=WBA Continental (Europe)<br>heavyweight champion\n|years=5 October 2013 \u2013 6 July 2014<br>Won world title}}\n{{s-vac|next=Otto Wallin}}\n{{s-bef|before=Jovo Pudar}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Pan Asian Boxing Association|PABA]] heavyweight ch