re}}</ref>\n|Shirley\n|Thriller by ''William Webb'' <ref>{{IMDb title|id=1034647|title=William Webb}}</ref>\n|-\n|1980\n|''[[Breaking Glass|Breaking Glass]]'' <ref>{{IMDb title|id=0080469|title=Breaking Glass}}</ref>\n|Kate\n|Drama Musical by ''Brian Gibson'' <ref>{{IMDb title|id=0001270|title=Brian Gibson}}</ref> - [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FKLp8Y5RlQ8 Official Film Trailer]\n|-\n|1982\n|''Jangles'' <ref>{{IMDb title|id=0376403|title=Jangles}}</ref>\n|Joanne\n|TV mini series (7 episodes) by ''HTV West'' <ref>{{IMDb title|id=0032564|title=HTV West}}</ref> \n|-\n|1983\n|\"[[Who's That Girl? (Eurythmics song)|Who's That Girl?]]\"\n|Herself\n|Music video (Eurythmics)\n|-\n|1986\n|''[[Prospects (TV series)|Prospects]]''  <ref>{{IMDb title|id=0134259|title=Prospects}}</ref>\n|Bev Reid\n|TV series (Episode 10 - Follow the Yellow Brick Lane) by ''Euston Films'' <ref>{{IMDb title|id=0103398|title=Euston Films}}</ref> - [https://www.imdb.com/video/vi2073863705?playlistId=tt0134259&ref_=tt_ov_vi Official Series Trailer]\n|-\n|1986\n|''[[Car Trouble (film)|Car Trouble]]'' <ref>{{IMDb title|id=0088883|title=Car Trouble}}</ref>\n|Maureen\n|Comedy by ''David Green'' <ref>{{IMDb title|id=0337765|title=David Green}}</ref>\n|-\n|1986\n|''Fighting Back'' <ref>{{IMDb title|id=0421336|title=Fighting Back}}</ref> \n|Viv Sharpe\n|TV mini series (5 episodes) by ''British Broadcasting Corporation (BBC)'' <ref>{{IMDb title|id=0043107|title=British Broadcasting Corporation (BBC)}}</ref>\n|-\n|1990\n|''Alive and Kicking in L.A.''\n|Herself\n|Documentary\n|-\n|2005\n|''Hazel O'Connor Live in Brighton'' \n|Herself\n|Live DVD including interview\n|-\n|2008\n|''Beyond The Breaking Glass'' \n|Herself\n|A limited release documenting O'Connor's life story in the style of her stage show ''Beyond The Breaking Glass''\n|-\n|2019\n|''Baghdad In My Shadow'' <ref>{{IMDb title|id=6864088|title=Baghdad In My Shadow}}</ref>\n|Kate\n|Thriller by ''Samir'' <ref>{{IMDb title|id=0759848|title=Samir}}</ref